Final Answer:

Here are three restaurants with vegan menus within a 20-minute walk of 50 Lexington Ave, New York, NY, along with their online pickup ordering pages:

1. Le Botaniste
   Address: 833 Lexington Ave, New York, NY 10065
   Online ordering: https://www.ubereats.com/store/le-botaniste-soho/Ij0Ld7oPTGmrRUTsXZJSdw

2. Vegan On The Fly
   Address: 1 E 48th St, New York, NY 10017
   Online ordering: https://veganontf.com

3. Urban Vegan Kitchen
   Address: 41 W 23rd St, New York, NY 10010
   Online ordering: https://www.ubereats.com/store/urban-vegan-kitchen-23rd-street/Ib7pTNJZRMmNPEFrHWgLZA

